---
const faq = [
  {
    question: "How do I get started with your SaaS platform?",
    answer:
      "Getting started is straightforward. Simply navigate to the 'Get Started' or 'Sign Up' section on our website, and follow the on-screen instructions to create your new account.",
  },
  {
    question: "What payment options are available?",
    answer:
      "We support a variety of payment methods including major credit cards, debit cards, PayPal, and in some cases, bank transfers. Select your preferred option during the subscription process.",
  },
  {
    question: "How do you protect my data?",
    answer:
      "Data protection is our top priority. We employ advanced encryption and security practices to safeguard your personal and professional information, ensuring compliance with global data protection regulations.",
  },
  {
    question: "Can I cancel my service subscription?",
    answer:
      "Yes, you are free to cancel your subscription at any moment. Simply access your account settings and navigate to the 'Manage Subscription' area to cancel.",
  },
  {
    question: "Is there a money-back guarantee?",
    answer:
      "Absolutely, we offer a 30-day money-back guarantee. If our service doesn’t meet your expectations within the first 30 days, you're eligible for a full refund.",
  },
  {
    question: "How can I reach customer support?",
    answer:
      "Our customer support team is available via email, live chat, and phone. Visit our 'Support' or 'Contact Us' page for more details and to get in touch.",
  },
  {
    question: "What are the technical requirements?",
    answer:
      "Our platform is accessible on most devices with internet connectivity and a modern web browser. For specific software or OS requirements, please refer to our 'Technical Requirements' section.",
  },
  {
    question: "Is it possible to upgrade my subscription plan?",
    answer:
      "Definitely. You can upgrade your plan anytime through your account dashboard under the 'Subscription' or 'Plan' settings, where you’ll find options for different subscription levels.",
  },
  {
    question: "Do you offer special pricing for non-profits?",
    answer:
      "Yes, we support non-profit organizations with special pricing plans. Reach out to our sales team for more details and eligibility criteria.",
  },

];
---

<section>
  <div class="max-w-screen-xl px-8 py-12 mx-auto md:px-12 lg:px-32">
    <div>
      <span
        class="font-mono text-xs font-medium tracking-tight text-blue-600 uppercase"
      >
        FAQ
      </span>
      <p
        class="mt-8 text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tighter lg:text-3xl text-blue-950"
      >
        Frquently asked questions <span
          class="md:block md:text-transparent md:bg-clip-text md:bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-indigo-600 py-2"
          >ready to be answered</span
        >
      </p>
      <p class="max-w-sm mt-4 text-base text-gray-700 lg:text-base">
        Explore a wide range of financial tools, features, and support for your
        financial goals and questions
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2 mt-10">
        <a
          href="/forms/contact"
          class="flex items-center justify-center h-10 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition-all duration-200 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-500 to-indigo-600 hover:to-indigo-700 shadow-button shadow-blue-600/50 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-950 focus:ring-offset-2 ring-offset-gray-200 hover:shadow-none"
          >Contact sales</a
        >
        <a
          href="/"
          class="flex items-center justify-center h-10 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-500 transition-all duration-200 bg-white border border-gray-300 rounded-full hover:text-blue-700 focus:ring-2 shadow-button shadow-gray-500/5 focus:ring-blue-950 focus:ring-offset-2 ring-offset-gray-200 hover:shadow-none"
          >See all pages</a
        >
      </div>
    </div>
    <div
      class="grid grid-cols-1 mt-12 gap-y-12 gap-x-4 lg:gap-x-12 md:grid-cols-2 "
    >
      {
        faq.map((faq) => (
          <>
            <div>
              <p class="font-mono text-balance text-base font-medium tracking-tighter uppercase">
                {faq.question}
              </p>
              <p class="mt-8 text-sm text-pretty text-gray-700">{faq.answer}</p>
            </div>
          </>
        ))
      }
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
